name: CUBETHON v1.5
description:
Hey there. This my first game. A CUBE sliding on platform. Avoid obstacle and dash through all the level. 

To make it more interesting, comment time taken by you to complete the game.

Controls :

  • A to move Left
  • D to move Right

Hope You Will Enjoy The Game!
